OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe son of Ian Coates, one of the
OL,8,Fvictims of the Nottingham attacks in
OL,9,FJune 2023, has spoken out following
OL,10,Fthe release of a report that exposes
OL,11,Fserious failings in the care of Valdo
OL,12,FCalocane.
OL,14,FJames Coates expressed his anger,
OL,15,Ffrustration and heartbreak to ITV News
OL,16,FCentral Correspondent Peter Bearne
OL,17,Fafter learning new details from the
OL,18,Freport - saying a catalogue of errors
OL,19,Fcould have prevented the brutal
OL,20,Fkillings.
