OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "You think you've
OL,8,Fheard it all," he said, before adding:
OL,9,F"Then more information comes out that
OL,10,Fdrags us straight through it all
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,F"To go through this report and see
OL,14,Fwhat could have been done to stop him
OL,15,Fit's just unbelievable, it's heart-
OL,16,Fwrenching,", he adds.
