OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCalocane, who had been diagnosed with
OL,8,Fparanoid schizophrenia, was sentenced
OL,9,Fto an indefinite hospital order after
OL,10,Fkilling 19-year-old students Barnaby
OL,11,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and 65-
OL,12,Fyear-old caretaker Ian Coates before
OL,13,Fattempting to kill three other people
OL,14,Fin June 2023.
OL,16,FThe report confirms concerns around
OL,17,Fthe handling of the attacker's mental
OL,18,Fhealth treatment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
