OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt details failures in risk
OL,8,Fassessments, miscommunication between
OL,9,Fagencies - and a culture of neglect
OL,10,Fwithin NHS Nottingham's mental health
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FIt was revealed the risk to staff who
OL,14,Flooked after him was "managed" by
OL,15,Fmaking arrangements so workers didn't
OL,16,Fvisit his home alone, but they didn't
OL,17,Fplan for the "hazards" if he came off
OL,18,Fhis medication and disengaged with
OL,19,Fmental health services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
