OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report detailed two years of
OL,8,Fviolent and disturbing behaviour from
OL,9,FCalocane, including frightening a
OL,10,Fneighbour so much she jumped out of a
OL,11,Ffirst-floor window, leading to a
OL,12,Fserious back injury, punching a police
OL,13,Fofficer in the face and holding his
OL,14,Fflatmates "hostage".
OL,16,FCoates said professionals tasked with
OL,17,Fsafeguarding the public failed in
OL,18,Ftheir duty.
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@SO]
