OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "This isn't a case
OL,8,Fof someone cutting corners or selling
OL,9,Fout-of-date food.
OL,11,F"This is about three people brutally
OL,12,Fmurdered and three others seriously
OL,13,Finjured because the NHS couldn't do
OL,14,Fits job properly," he said.
OL,16,FThe attacker had a long history of
OL,17,Fviolent behaviour, including incidents
OL,18,Fin which he was tasered, pepper-
OL,19,Fsprayed, and required frequent
OL,20,Frestraint and medication.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
