OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHowever, Coates said, the authorities
OL,8,Fclassified him as only a "medium"
OL,9,Fthreat to the public.
OL,11,F"From the very beginning, there were
OL,12,Fmassive red flags. The way he acted
OL,13,Ftowards police officers, the way he
OL,14,Fhad to be restrained - it was all
OL,15,Fthere. And still, he wasn't assessed
OL,16,Fproperly," he said.
OL,18,FCoates and his family are now calling
OL,19,Ffor urgent action to prevent future
OL,20,Ftragedies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
