OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe said: "There can't be another quick
OL,8,Fapology and a promise to do better.
OL,9,FThere has to be real change,".
OL,11,FHe believes the attacker should face a
OL,12,Fprison sentence for his crimes once
OL,13,Fhis mental health treatment is
OL,14,Fcomplete.
OL,16,F"I understand he needs hospital
OL,17,Ftreatment, but when he's stable, he
OL,18,Fneeds to be punished for what he did,"
OL,19,FCoates said.
