OL,3,CSon calls for accountability after
OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FWith a judge-led public inquiry now in
OL,8,Fmotion, Coates hopes the damning
OL,9,Freport will accelerate efforts to hold
OL,10,Fthose responsible accountable.
OL,12,FHe said: "The sooner this inquiry gets
OL,13,Funderway, the sooner we can start
OL,14,Fmaking people answer for their actions.
OL,16,F"My dad should still be here. If just
OL,17,Fone thing had been done differently,
OL,18,Fthis could have had a whole different
OL,19,Foutcome."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
