OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FNHS officials published the full
OL,8,Freport after initially saying they
OL,9,Fwould only publish a summary due to
OL,10,Fdata protection issues.
OL,12,FDr Jessica Sokolov, regional medical
OL,13,Fdirector at NHS England (Midlands),
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's clear the system got it
OL,15,Fwrong, including the NHS, and the
OL,16,Fconsequences of when this happens can
OL,17,Fbe devastating.
