OL,7,F"This is not acceptable, and I
OL,8,Funreservedly apologise to the families
OL,9,Fof victims on behalf of the NHS and
OL,10,Fthe organisations involved in
OL,11,Fdelivering care to Valdo Calocane
OL,12,Fbefore this incident took place."
