OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FClaire Murdoch, NHS England's national
OL,8,Fmental health director, said: "It is
OL,9,Fclear there were failings in the care
OL,10,Fprovided to Valdo Calocane, which is
OL,11,Fwhy the trust responsible was placed
OL,12,Fin our highest oversight and support
OL,13,Fprogramme, which has seen them
OL,14,Foverhaul their risk assessment
OL,15,Fprocesses.
OL,26,@pD@_OU
