OL,4,Cfailings revealed in 'heart-wrenching'
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Nationally, we have asked every
OL,8,Fmental health trust to review these
OL,9,Ffindings and set out action plans for
OL,10,Fhow they treat and engage with people
OL,11,Fwho have a serious mental illness,
OL,12,Fincluding how they work with other
OL,13,Fagencies such as the police.
OL,15,F"And we've instructed trusts not to
OL,16,Fdischarge people if they do not attend
OL,17,Fappointments.
